    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.100.116759.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Distribution records of Pholcus spiders from the Qinling Mountains in this study. The Pholcus bidentatus group: 1 P. bidentatus; the crypticolens group: 2 P. jingyangensis, 3 P. langensis, 4 P. manueli, 5 P. zichyi; the Pholcus taishan group: 6 P. jiaozuo sp. nov., 7 P. yugong; the Pholcus yichengicus group: 8 P. luonan sp. nov., 9 P. luoyang sp. nov., 10 P. lushan sp. nov., 11 P. ovatus, 12 P. parayichengicus, 13 P. shangluo sp. nov., 14 P. songxian, 15 P. taibaiensis, 16 P. tangyuensis, 17 P. weinan sp. nov., 18 P. yuncheng sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/992469" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.100.116759.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Pholcus shangluo sp. nov., holotype male A, B. Palp (A. Prolateral view; B. Retrolateral view); C, D. Distal part of procursus (C. Prolateral view, arrow points at thick part; D. Dorsal view, arrow points at straight part). Scale bars: 0.20 mm (A, B); 0.10 mm (C, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/992478" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.100.116759.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Pholcus shangluo sp. nov., holotype male (C-F) and paratype female (A, B, G, H) A. Epigyne, ventral view; B. Vulva, dorsal view; C. Bulbal apophyses, prolateral view; D. Chelicerae, frontal view; E-H. Habitus (E, G. Dorsal view; F. Lateral view; H. Ventral view). Scale bars: 0.20 mm (A-D); 1.00 mm (E-H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/992479" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

